dct_title_s: Map showing a portion of Beach Thoroughfare adjoining Atlantic City, NJ III
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Brighton Avenue to Arkansas Avenue along Beach Thoroughfare in Atlantic City. Map shows high and low water lines. West Jersey and Seashore Railroad pictured. Pleasantville and A.C. Turnpike shown. Atlantic City Railroad shown. Multiple companies and estates pictured.
